title: Travelers scramble in Puerto Vallarta as Hurricane Patricia nears
text: BING NEWS: Travelers scramble in Puerto Vallarta as Hurricane Patricia nears (CNN)The rapid approach of Category 5 Hurricane Patricia has resort areas along Mexico's Pacific coast rushing to safeguard guests from the strongest hurricane ever recorded.
